{"tid":658722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中興供應鏈斷裂或已在華停售智慧手機 中蟈或成最大贏家","createTime":"2018-05-09T08:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T11:38:13.000Z","uid":35774,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ae714fed2d7eb502e76e29a3a4a8d6570b5e79fe","tid":658722,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1525838814390&amp;issue=20180509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1525838814390%26issue%3D20180509&d=Wasgvqq%2BsjEdEnWNDSVYoIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=721b05d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1525838814390%26issue%3D20180509&h=9b97fd6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1525838814390&amp;issue=20180509</a><br />\n<br />\n日媒：中興或已在華停售智慧手機 (11:56)<br />\n文章日期：2018年5月9日<br />\n<br />\n中興通訊（0763）上月受到美國商務部制裁，美國企業停止向其供應零部件，令中興陷入「休克」狀態。《日本經濟新聞》報導，中興或已在內地停售智慧手機，位於深圳總部內的直營店內的商品已經下架，官方網上銷售亦已停止。美國啟動制裁至今已過去3周，中興的智慧手機銷售陷入困難局面。<br />\n<br />\n此外，天貓ZTE中興官方旗艦店頁面顯示「網站改版中」，已經無法下單。雖然目前通信運營商經營的智慧手機銷售店仍有出售中興產品，但有消息人士表示中興的產品基本上已沒有庫存。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">厲害了，蛾的蟈</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631f25256e0bebd359154c1d851b04e2e6c3d733","tid":658722,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80be8fda927878b19678fa811e91b05bfc300fc5","tid":658722,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:31:51.000Z","msg":"【傳中興正推動出售手機業務】有媒體稱，因受美國禁令影響，中興正在推動出售手機業務。中興終端方面目前暫未對此置評。<br />\n<br />\n咁都賣得出？"},{"pid":"ea4f9ea8cd7bd35c7aae89ee130e875f4f61fec5","tid":658722,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:40:30.000Z","msg":"犯我支那者<br />\n雖遠必豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64eba837b2efc9448828bb3da4eea1b1ce755b7d","tid":658722,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60df25c85e7be95e45d55a244a9597fa9f517c1d","tid":658722,"uid":126711,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【傳中興正推動出售手機業務】有媒體稱，因受美國禁令影響，中興正在推動出售手機業務。中興終端方面目前暫未對此置評。<br />\n<br />\n咁都賣得出？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n博物館堆買手"},{"pid":"a04f56dda633aa42716960333a4c94f2da7a5ed1","tid":658722,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4534c74b61266f6e0deee34533af83a044e1ff","tid":658722,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b0f291a3122c24c4bb6881ec971b22e23839b856","tid":658722,"uid":11428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/SEHK/2018/0509/LTN20180509720_C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2FSEHK%2F2018%2F0509%2FLTN20180509720_C.pdf&d=Wasgvqq%2BsjEdEnWNDSVYoIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=3240b9b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/SEHK/2018/0509/LTN20180509720_C.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nGG 了"},{"pid":"d3e4539775d98511c88f05e4e7b9941aac0368e3","tid":658722,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:38:13.000Z","msg":"轉走晒資產，淨番個殼<br />\n股東仆街了"}]}